Still we try, ALL OF US have our own paths we cling to Still we try, ALL OF US have our own paths we cling to

35
00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:48.550
ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you

36
00:01:47.550 --> 00:01:49.080
ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you ALL OF US, I've got something to tell you If you've got a dream that's worth a damn you've gotta stand tall If you've got a dream that's worth a damn you've gotta stand tall If you've got a dream that's worth a damn you've gotta stand tall

